name: Dimension Jumper (YankiDev)
description:
Made in 5 hours for Quad Jam 3: Time Loop x Mini Worlds.

Might add better visuals on Friday or might now depends if I have time sorry for the visuals and lack of content.

A, D, SPACE - move left, right and jump 

M - Freeze time to jump between dimensions 

W, S - While the time is frozen jump between dimensions
